        "title": "fix(anthropic): add haiku catalog entry",
        "body": "Fixes #90088.\n\n## What changed\n\n- Adds Claude Haiku 4.5 to the Anthropic provider-owned static model catalog.\n- Keeps resolution logic unchanged; this only fills the missing static catalog row for the `anthropic` api_key provider path.\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\nSetup:\n\n- Repository: OpenClaw checkout.\n- Branch under test: `fastino-90088-haiku-model`.\n- Proof script imports the real bundled static catalog resolver from `src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/model.static-catalog.ts` and resolves `anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5-20251001` against each checkout's actual bundled plugin manifest.\n\nBefore, on current main:\n\n```text\nnode_modules/.bin/tsx /private/tmp/openclaw-90088-proof.ts /Users/allahyar/Documents/fastino-tasks/openclaw\nnull\n```\n\nAfter, on this branch:\n\n```text\nnode_modules/.bin/tsx /private/tmp/openclaw-90088-proof.ts /Users/allahyar/Documents/fastino-tasks/openclaw-tui-90088b\n{\n  \"provider\": \"anthropic\",\n  \"id\": \"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\n  \"name\": \"Claude Haiku 4.5\",\n  \"contextWindow\": 200000,\n  \"maxTokens\": 64000,\n  \"input\": [\n    \"text\",\n    \"image\"\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## Verification\n\n```text\ngit diff --check -- extensions/anthropic/openclaw.plugin.json\n```\n\nNo output.\n\n```text\nnode scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/model.static-catalog.test.ts src/agents/model-catalog.test.ts packages/model-catalog-core/src/provider-model-id-normalization.test.ts\n\n[test] starting test/vitest/vitest.unit.config.ts\nTest Files  1 passed (1)\nTests  5 passed (5)\n\n[test] starting test/vitest/vitest.agents.config.ts\nTest Files  2 passed (2)\nTests  44 passed (44)\n\n[test] passed 2 Vitest shards in 7.76s\n```\n\n## Platforms tested\n\n- macOS local checkout with Node 26 and repository test runner.\n\n## Limitations\n\n- This proves the source-level static catalog resolution path; it does not make a live Anthropic API request.\n",
